Package: variantsinvestigator
Type: Package
Title: VCF to SQLite Converter and Variants Visualization Tool
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Francesco Lescai
Maintainer: Francesco Lescai <francesco.lescai@gmail.com>
Description: Provides tools to convert VCF files into SQLite databases and a Shiny application to visualize, filter, and analyze the variants. It includes filtering by quality, impact, frequency, and custom gene lists.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
LazyDataCompression: xz
